INSERT INTO public."Review" VALUES ('cmnkctw420011plhpr4qo9diy', 'fontaines-dc-vicar-street-march-2026', 'Fontaines D.C. Bring the House Down at Vicar Street', 'Fontaines D.C.', 'Vicar Street', 'Dublin', '2026-03-10 00:00:00', 'In ar gCroithe go deo, Big Shot, Favourite, Starburster, Romance', 'What a night. Fontaines D.C. returned to Vicar Street with the kind of intensity that reminds you why live music matters.
INSERT INTO public."Review" VALUES ('cmnkctw450012plhpvokw9drr', 'lankum-national-concert-hall-feb-2026', 'Lankum''s Transcendent Night at the National Concert Hall', 'Lankum', 'National Concert Hall', 'Dublin', '2026-02-22 00:00:00', 'Go Dig My Grave, Netta Pradesh, The Granite Gaze, Bear Creek', 'There''s something almost spiritual about seeing Lankum in the National Concert Hall.
INSERT INTO public."Review" VALUES ('cmnkctw480013plhpwn5o7mjk', 'murder-capital-whelans-jan-2026', 'The Murder Capital at Whelan''s — Raw and Relentless', 'The Murder Capital', 'Whelan''s', 'Dublin', '2026-01-18 00:00:00', 'Existence, Return My Head, Ethel, Don''t Cling to Life', 'Sometimes a small venue gig is exactly what you need. The Murder Capital at Whelan''s was sweaty, loud, and brilliant.
